        "Title": "Eviction Notice",
        "Location": "LOCATION_COASTALTOWN_EBOLA",
        "PublicId": "115542678321",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_PRO/Scenes/Missions/CoastalTown/scene_ebola.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository e9cdd276-328a-4aaf-8a1a-d372556980ce).Image",
        "Description": "Good evening, 47. Sapienza has an unfortunate squatter problem, with several offenders illegally overstaying in otherwise occupied houses. Our client has decided to send lawyer Salvatore Bravuomo to evict them, but he has chickened out and is hiding in his office. \r\rIf we can&apos;t convince Mr Bravuomo, let&apos;s deal with the squatters ourselves. We can even pick up Mr Bravuomo&apos;s check along the way if he is seen entering the affected houses. I&apos;ll leave you to prepare.",
